                <ol class="lead">
                    <li><strong>Look for the TLC blue diamond decals</strong>: located in each rear passenger door, the windshield, and the rear door window.</li>
                    <li><strong>Have a look at the plate</strong>: TLC-issued license plates either begin with T and end with C, or end with either: LV, LB, LA, or BB.</li>
